This stage uses a sound meter from the sound system as an image map.
Specify 'waveform' to get a scope rather than bars.

Description
-----------

The **soundMap** keyword renders a visual representation of sounds,
played by the entity to which this material is assigned, into a buffer.

Usage
-----

    soundMap [type]

Parameters
----------

-   [type] = The type of visualization to render.
    -   [meter] = Renders a series of bars.
    -   [waveform] = Renders a waveform.

Example
-------

Render a waveform...

    {
       soundMap waveform
    }

Notes
-----

Not Available.

